te/incomplete state\\n* Delete individual task\\n* Persist tasks after page refresh via `localStorage`\\n* Mobile-friendly layout\\n* No external frameworks\\n\\nCommit with the message:\\n`'Generate Todo App'`"}	2026-03-27 10:46:57.09199+00	\N
